Twelve señoras and eight young men through the school of cuadros — bookkeeping, assembly law, how to speak to a functionary without blinking. Within a year, half the east side's committees are chaired by graduates. The Party did not capture the movement. It did something the DFS's categories cannot file: it became part of how the movement thinks.
